    • Constructor Detail

      • Principal_Angles

        public Principal_Angles(Jama.Matrix m)
        Constructor to compute the principal angles between two equidimensional subspaces of a vector space. This class takes as input the matrix of inner products between the two orthonormal bases. If the two subspaces are 20 dimensional, the matrix of inner products will be a 20 x 20 square symmetric matrix
        Parameters:
        m - The matrix of inner products (projections).
